org.apache.ambari.server.controller.internal

Class Extension

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ambari.server.controller.internal.Extension

  • public class Extension
extends Object
    Encapsulates extension information. An extension version is like a stack version but it contains custom services. Linking an extension version to the current stack version allows the cluster to install the custom services contained in the extension version.
